This week I was inducted into the @odeahighschool Class of 2023 Wall of Honor. 

For those that know the athletic powerhouse that O’Dea is, and the talented young men it has produced know what an honor it is to be among the other men on that wall! 

I want to thank everyone for coming out and being a part of this great celebration both for me and my family. Was truly special to have my kids there along side me. A special thank you to Coach Kohler and @wizdom80 for working with me and my schedule to make this possible!
